=================================================
JUSTINMOSS.NET — BRAND GUIDELINES (QUICK REF)
=================================================

Last updated: 2026-01-27

This is a practical reference file.
If it's not here, it’s not locked yet.


-------------------------------------------------
BRAND / SITE
-------------------------------------------------

Primary site: justinmoss.net
Structure: Single site with multiple “collections”
Tone: Personal, reflective, exploratory (not polished-corporate)

Collections may override accent colors, but share core typography
and base neutrals unless explicitly changed.


-------------------------------------------------
TYPOGRAPHY
-------------------------------------------------

Headings:
- Font: Outfit
- Weight: Bold
- Usage: H1–H6, section titles, emphasis text

Body:
- Font: Inter
- Weight: Regular (400)
- Usage: Paragraphs, lists, UI text, captions

Notes:
- Keep typography simple and consistent
- No decorative fonts
- Let color + spacing do the work


-------------------------------------------------
CORE NEUTRAL COLORS (SITEWIDE)
-------------------------------------------------

Headings / Dark Elements:
- #1C1C1E  (Deep charcoal black)

Body Text / Secondary Dark:
- #3A3A3C  (Soft dark gray)

These neutrals are shared across all collections
unless explicitly overridden.


-------------------------------------------------
COLLECTION COLOR SYSTEM
-------------------------------------------------

Each collection uses 3 accent colors.
Accents are layered on top of the core neutrals.


DEFAULT (Base / Fallback)
---------------------------------
Accent 1: #E8EFFF
Accent 2: #6B8CFF
Accent 3: #1F3FBF


ADHDMAZING
---------------------------------
Accent 1 (lightest):  #AEE9F5
Accent 2 (medium):    #4FB2C7
Accent 3 (darkest):   #176072

Notes:
- adhdmazing is always lowercase
- Calm, supportive, non-alarming tone


ITMIGHTBEME
---------------------------------
Accent 1: #FFE2D3
Accent 2: #C46A2F
Accent 3: #7A3C14


EPIPHILY (Faith / Reflection)
---------------------------------
Accent 1: #F3ECD7
Accent 2: #B89B4F
Accent 3: #6B5621


CENTERLINE
---------------------------------
Accent 1: #DDE9FF
Accent 2: #3F74D8
Accent 3: #1C3C7F


-------------------------------------------------
USAGE NOTES
-------------------------------------------------

- Neutrals stay consistent sitewide
- Accents are used for:
  - Links
  - Buttons
  - Dividers
  - Emphasis elements
- Avoid overusing Accent 3 (darkest)
- White space is intentional


-------------------------------------------------
